{
  "stem": "25598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came out and-- well, he helped the bakers for a while and then eventually, I don't know if whatever they-- there demands were, [? worries ?] or not, but eventually the men were let out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I guess because I was so young, I really don't remember the flow of the whole story.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember separate incidents from the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I, I don't exactly know when this happened, and when the other happened, and how they all fit together.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next thing I remember was announcements at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since not many people had radios-- or a telephone, of course, was unheard of-- the announcements from the city hall were made by somebody coming out on the stairs of the city hall and drumming.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that meant that the population has to gather around, and they would make all kinds of announcements.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Announcements about wearing the yellow star, or about curfews, or about what have you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in October-- [CLEARS THROAT] OK, my birthday is in September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I turned 10 in September '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I expected it to be as it usually was, a lot of fun, and a lot of gifts, and the-- the party, and all of that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was not the case.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, some of my, my aunts even forgot to buy me presents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knew there was something very wrong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know what, what it is, but I knew that there's something very wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a short while after that, about a week or 10 days after that, the drummer made the announcement that all Jews from the city have to gather in the afternoon at the train station.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
